        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider font-black">What nobody tells jewelry stores about websites</p>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-amber-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
