              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Store hid prices. Added clear pricing: "Engagement Rings: $1,000-10,000" with ranges. Month 1: 67% more qualified purchases. Price transparency = can afford = serious buyer.</p>
            </div>
