      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-4">Build Your Jewelry Store Website</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">Choose based on e-commerce needs and product showcase requirements.</p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8">
        <a href="/reviews/squarespace-ai" class="block p-6 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/20">
